  <brief_title>Sequential Use of Low-dose Sunitinib With Chemotherapy in Advanced NSCLC After Failure of Conventional Regimen</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study of Efficacy and Safety of Sequential Low-dose Sunitinib With Chemotherapy in Advanced Non-small Cell Lung Cancer After Failure of Conventional Regimen</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
