  </sponsors>
  <source>Chinese Academy of Medical Sciences</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether sequential application of low-dose
      short-term sunitinib and chemotherapy is effective in the treatment of non-small cell lung
      cancer after failure of conventional therapy. Safety of this regimen will also be evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
